{"tid":1303004,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[勁過鄭俊英]《小神的孩子們》男主姜至奐被緊急逮捕 涉嫌強姦&性侵2名女職員","createTime":"2019-07-10T06:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T09:39:09.000Z","uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0361c4a2920a5d9e6c3c2e4b54b6f608b09712","tid":1303004,"uid":238483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"韓劇《錢的戰爭》、《小神的孩子們》的男主角姜至奐因涉嫌性侵，於7月9日晚間在其光州家中被緊急逮捕。<br />\n據光州警方透露，姜志奐當天和經紀公司的兩名女職員在員工聚餐後，繼續到自己家裡喝酒。 當晚他進入<span style=\"color: red;\">兩位女性睡覺的房間，對A某實施性侵</span>，並對B某進行性騷擾。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-07-10/118259-751292.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-07-10%2F118259-751292.png&h=d213784b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA某於當晚9點41分給在首爾的朋友發了短訊，說自己在姜至奐家裡喝酒，還被對方關在房間裡，求朋友幫忙報警。 警方到達後，她表示在睡覺時遭到性侵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-07-10/118259-751289.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-07-10%2F118259-751289.png&h=9802705e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姜至奐稱記得自己喝了酒，之後發生的事完全沒有印象，醒來之後發現自己在女職員的房間裡。 警方表示今天（7月10日）將再次傳喚姜至奐繼續調查。<br />\nAV情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8011082d0373576a86eae8bd9a724907554f2b5d","tid":1303004,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T06:55:36.000Z","msg":"帶番屋企開餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020d69c7f826de975c5f3f224e9fee713507898b","tid":1303004,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"我又唔信件事係男方單方面囉..."},{"pid":"4f6825a45bdac54d3d0b3a751d99b6f6c82fc5a6","tid":1303004,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"人渣"},{"pid":"29bd7e5513d375